{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d6e1c5636f","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"924f8e44a2","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"d6e1c5636f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"8127264065","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄炎培，民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"},{"id":"9a1fa4bada","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄炎培1951年12月28日给毛泽东的信。信中谈到轻工业部三反运动的一些具体情况，说在向商店查请中，发现不少漏税、行赌、送回扣的情况，民建总会及北京市分会正在展开工商界思想改造运动，预备提出“消灭行随、消灭回扣”的口号，回扣实是贪污，在北京社会根深蒂固，不扑灭，无以整伤各机关风纪。"},{"id":"6fa51ff65f","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄炎培1951年12月8日在轻工业部全体工作人员大会上的报告，题为《我们要彻底地为反贫污反浪费反官像主义而斗争》。后在1951年12月30日《人民日报》上发表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"14e8383fbc","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"8127264065","type":"paragraph","text":"黄先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"9a1fa4bada","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十八日惠书敬悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"6fa51ff65f","type":"paragraph","text":"轻工业部发动反贪污反浪费反官主义斗争，并已开始收效，甚为欣感。讲演稿很好，只须将第一面有四处括号内数字去掉，就可发表。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"8281c3df79","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"0bf3ee1eec","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"},{"id":"feadc6ddd7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十二月廿九日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f"}],"page":{"id":"5288c3a4cc","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"d6e1c5636f","start":197,"end":197}}}},"__N_SSG":true}